1
00:00:17,560 --> 00:00:18,320
Excuse me,

2
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:20,000
may I ask

3
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:21,520
when the special exhibition

4
00:00:21,520 --> 00:00:22,720
by Era Gallery

5
00:00:22,720 --> 00:00:23,880
will be held?

6
00:00:23,880 --> 00:00:24,720
What special exhibition?

7
00:00:27,080 --> 00:00:29,000
We will fully cooperate with Mr. James's team

8
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:30,080
to implement the specific exhibition plan

9
00:00:30,080 --> 00:00:31,920
of Era Gallery.

10
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:32,920
Please rest assured.

11
00:00:33,320 --> 00:00:33,800
Okay.

12
00:00:33,800 --> 00:00:34,560
Thank you.

13
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:35,440
Thank you very much.

14
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:53,880
That's great, James.

15
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:55,000
I just asked.

16
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:55,640
The venue said

17
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:57,040
they would fully cooperate with us.

18
00:00:57,040 --> 00:00:57,680
It's our duty.

19
00:00:57,680 --> 00:00:58,520
I'll see you out.

20
00:00:58,520 --> 00:00:59,040
Okay.

21
00:01:01,480 --> 00:01:02,280
Thank you, Forester Lin.

22
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:03,360
See you at the special exhibition.

23
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:04,160
Okay.

24
00:01:06,360 --> 00:01:07,760
You should be made permanent next time.

25
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:08,240
Thank you.

26
00:01:09,560 --> 00:01:10,240
James,

27
00:01:10,240 --> 00:01:10,920
what should I

28
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:11,840
wear tomorrow?

29
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:13,400
Who are they?

30
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:15,280
Don't you know?

31
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,760
They called you Forester Lin.

32
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:18,800
I thought you were from our museum.

33
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,480
Mr. Zhen.

34
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:30,960
Stop me.

35
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:32,280
Do you know who I am?

36
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:38,520
Boss Zhen.

37
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:39,920
Last time at the auction house,

38
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:41,880
I had to let go of the Heart of Black Diamond

39
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:43,480
with great reluctance.

40
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:44,920
Next time, if there's any treasure,

41
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,240
think of me.

42
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:48,480
Young Master Zhang, you are really humorous.

43
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:50,760
Your Zhang Group is a big business.

44
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,720
What do I have

45
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:52,960
that could catch your eye?

46
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:53,720
There really is.

47
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,360
The Vanishing Rose...

48
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:56,800
No.

49
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:58,640
The Vanishing Rose is a good one.

50
00:01:58,640 --> 00:01:59,800
How about selling it to me?

51
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,920
Young Master Zhang, you must be kidding.

52
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:05,960
The Vanishing Rose

53
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:07,960
is the highlight of our Era Gallery's

54
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:09,960
joint exhibition with He Art Museum

55
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,560
this time.

56
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:12,800
Joint exhibition?

57
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:16,400
Ye Zhiqiu told me about it.

58
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:19,480
I didn't expect the liar to make it.

59
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,520
Liar?

60
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,600
That curator

61
00:02:22,600 --> 00:02:23,760
is a fake,

62
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:26,040
just relying on his connections with He Xiaochen

63
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:27,320
to swindle people outside.

64
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:30,160
Young Master Zhang,

65
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:31,800
I have something else to do.

66
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,560
Excuse me.

67
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,160
He Art Museum.

68
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,000
Wait.

69
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:37,880
I

70
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:39,000
happened to not drive a car.

71
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,000
Could you give me a ride?

72
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:41,880
You...

73
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,440
Move this a little bit.

74
00:02:49,640 --> 00:02:50,280
That painting.

75
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:50,880
Teacher Ye.

76
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,200
The security system

77
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,600
has been adjusted to the highest level.

78
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:10,360
You're really something, He.

79
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,840
So considerate.

80
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,920
There are security guards here

81
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:13,720
patrolling every night.

82
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:15,400
With the infrared anti-theft device,

83
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:17,240
it can be said to be foolproof.

84
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,120
Thank you for your hard work.

85
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:19,840
James,

86
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:21,400
tomorrow is a big day.

87
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,160
Make sure

88
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,480
nothing goes wrong.

89
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:24,480
Don't worry.

90
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:26,080
Tomorrow is also a big day for you.

91
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,000
See you tomorrow.

92
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,280
He's gone.

93
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,680
Shall we start moving the paintings?

94
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,520
Let's do it.

95
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,320
Get to work.

96
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:50,080
Not bad, huh?

97
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,600
I knew it.

98
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:54,040
You're a big liar.

99
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,160
If you come later,

100
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:05,760
I tell you,

101
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:07,040
you move these things by yourself.

102
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:08,000
I won't.

103
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,680
Let me introduce again.

104
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:14,240
The Zhang Group's Young Master, Zhang Xiaoshao.

105
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,280
The sponsor you haven't met,

106
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,680
the one who planned to sponsor.

107
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:23,800
My partner,

108
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:24,600
Jia Yu.

109
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,280
Just call me Zhang.

110
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:27,400
Nice to meet you.

111
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,760
I told you to keep an eye on Zhen Shida.

112
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:31,000
What's going on with him?

113
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,120
Don't mention it.

114
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,280
If it weren't for me,

115
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:35,520
who is full of stratagems and courage,

116
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:37,640
the one standing here would be Zhen Shida.

117
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:40,360
Such a big boss,

118
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,560
in the middle of the night,

119
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:43,080
still has to go to the art museum in person.

120
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:46,480
Those are all my personal collections of famous paintings.

121
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:47,960
I can't be careless.

122
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:53,120
Hello?

123
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:53,720
Mom.

124
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,600
It's not that easy to find.

125
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,080
You definitely didn't find it.

126
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:58,760
You need to understand art

127
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:00,800
and have the ability.

128
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:02,280
Where do you find such a person?

129
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:05,200
Wait.

130
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,000
I think I have a candidate.

131
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:12,160
I negotiated down the price of several paintings

132
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,200
to get Zhen Shida

133
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,600
to my collection house.

134
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,840
That scoundrel got a great deal.

135
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:18,960
That's really going to cost Young Master Zhang

136
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:20,440
a lot of money.

137
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:21,520
Just keep it in mind.

138
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:35,040
Let me tell you,

139
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,720
your cooling system

140
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,840
has serious issues.

141
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:39,000
If it runs all day,

142
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,240
the oil paintings will all melt.

143
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,480
Can you take responsibility for that?

144
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:43,000
So we must close the gallery for a day tomorrow.

145
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:43,880
I need a day to check them.

146
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,480
Such high quality.

147
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:49,200
I dare not say it's a fake.

148
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:52,120
Who dares to say it's a fake?

149
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:03,920
All settled?

150
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,240
Yes.

151
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,960
Including "The Vanishing Rose",

152
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:08,760
there are 86 paintings in total.

153
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:09,600
All loaded on the truck.

154
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:11,920
Young Master Zhang is guarding them.

155
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:19,520
What a beautiful scenery.

156
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:24,000
The photos I sent you.

157
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,000
include a photo of you and my brother.

158
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,760
It was taken right here.

159
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:28,960
Do you remember?

160
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:40,720
You mean this one?

161
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:44,840
So,

162
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:46,680
Hao Feng also liked paintings.

163
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:58,600
These are all the photos

164
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:01,480
I have of your brother.

165
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:03,800
He loved looking at paintings,

166
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:06,000
even if he didn't always understand them.

167
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,520
He said

168
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:11,200
art is a sensual gift,

169
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,160
but he only understands rational data.

170
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:16,960
Maybe that's why

171
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,920
he can't understand the complexity of human hearts.

172
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:29,160
So Hao Feng

173
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:32,480
is a very simple and kind person.

174
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:34,520
Because he's too trusting,

175
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:37,160
he got deceived.

176
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,920
I failed to protect him.

177
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:44,720
Haven't you been by his side,

178
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,600
taking care of him?

179
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:47,080
Three years,

180
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:49,160
over a thousand days,

181
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:49,960
you were inseparable.

182
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:52,000
You know his habits

183
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,120
better than I do.

184
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:59,120
When we were young, our parents divorced,

185
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,200
and each took one child.

186
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,600
We were separated by the ocean

187
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,520
and lost contact.

188
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,160
I never thought that when we met again,

189
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,680
it would be a farewell to death.

190
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:10,960
I'm sorry.

191
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,160
If I could remember

192
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,520
some of our past experiences,

193
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,680
maybe I could tell you

194
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,000
something about him.

195
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:23,960
After I got in touch with him again,

196
00:08:23,960 --> 00:08:25,320
he often mentioned you in his emails.

197
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:31,400
He thought

198
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,640
you were his best friend.

199
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:42,640
Don't worry.

200
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:44,680
I won't let Zhen Shida get away with it.

201
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:47,200
We will get back every penny

202
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,960
those victims were scammed.

203
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,160
I think

204
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:55,480
that's also Hao Feng's wish.

205
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:01,280
Then let's hurry up.

206
00:09:01,560 --> 00:09:03,320
Let's get started.

207
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:20,720
Today's VIP exhibition

208
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:23,120
is just for some peers to visit.

209
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:23,800
Not to mention

210
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:25,800
when it opens to the public tomorrow,

211
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:27,800
it will be a sensation throughout the city.

212
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:30,200
Mr. Hao, you're too kind.

213
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:31,920
Actually, these paintings...

214
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:33,120
Ms. Ye.

215
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:33,760
Hello.

216
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:35,320
Hello.

217
00:09:35,760 --> 00:09:36,760
I'm here to see the exhibition

218
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:37,520
on behalf of Zhang's Gallery.

219
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:38,440
Our young master

220
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,440
is very busy today

221
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,760
and can't come to congratulate you.

222
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:42,120
He asked me to express his apologies.

223
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:43,480
I'm flattered.

224
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,280
I hope our peers

225
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,480
can give me more advice.

226
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,360
The collections of Era Gallery

227
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,720
are familiar to us.

228
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:51,080
Instead,

229
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,320
interested in

230
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:53,720
Ms. Ye's work.

231
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:54,520
Really?

232
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:57,440
As a professional curator,

233
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,520
I believe

234
00:09:58,520 --> 00:09:59,520
you will become

235
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:00,880
a world-renowned artist.

236
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,120
Thank you.

237
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:02,840
Ms. Ye,

238
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,120
here's my business card.

239
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:05,440
Keep in touch.

240
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,800
That's great, Ms. Ye.

241
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:09,320
It's time to consider my own career.

242
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:10,800
Ms. Ye,

243
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:11,840
I have some questions

244
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:12,960
I'd like to ask you.

245
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,080
Let's talk over here.

246
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:14,520
This way.
